Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBGroupPermissions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBGroupPermissions
  • public class JDBGroupPermissions
extends java.lang.Object
    JDBGroupPermissions class is used to insert/update and delete records from the SYS_GROUP_PERMISSIONS table. This table links the modules which a user is allowed to access to the group(s) which they belong to.

    See Also:
    JDBGroupPermissions, JDBGroup, JDBModule
